WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Examiner: Reset your baseline.

00:02.000 --> 00:05.000
Examiner: And blood black nothingness began to spin.

00:07.000 --> 00:10.000
Examiner: A system of cells interlinked within cells,

00:10.000 --> 00:13.000
Examiner: interlinked within cells, interlinked within one stem.

00:13.000 --> 00:15.000
man walking past: Fuck off.

00:13.000 --> 00:15.000
Examiner: Good job.

00:16.000 --> 00:19.000
Examiner: And dreadfully distinct against the dark,

00:19.000 --> 00:21.000
Examiner: a tall white fountain plate.

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
<i>[beeping begins]</i>

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
Examiner: Cells.
K: Cells.

00:24.000 --> 00:27.000
Examiner: Have you ever been in an institution?
K: Cells. Cells.

00:27.000 --> 00:29.000
Examiner: Do they keep you in a cell?
K: Cells. Cells.

00:29.000 --> 00:33.000
Examiner: When you're not performing your duties, do they keep you in a little box?
K: Cells.

00:33.000 --> 00:35.000
K: Cells. Interlinked. Interlinked.

00:35.000 --> 00:38.000
Examiner: What's it like to hold the hand of someone you love?
K: Interlinked.

00:38.000 --> 00:41.000
Examiner: Do they teach you how to feel? Finger to finger?
K: Interlinked.

00:41.000 --> 00:44.000
Examiner: Do you long for having your heart interlinked?
K: Interlinked.

00:44.000 --> 00:47.000
Examiner: Do you dream about being interlinked?
K: Interlinked.

00:47.000 --> 00:50.000
Examiner: What's it like to hold your child in your arms?
K: Interlinked.

00:50.000 --> 00:53.000
Examiner: Do you feel that there's a part of you that's missing?
K: Interlinked.

00:53.000 --> 00:56.000
K: Within cells interlinked. Within cells interlinked.

00:56.000 --> 00:58.000
Examiner: Why don't you say that three times?
K: Within cells interlinked.

00:58.000 --> 01:00.000
K: Within cells interlinked.

01:00.000 --> 01:02.000
K: Within cells interlinked.

01:02.000 --> 01:04.000
K: Within cells interlinked.

01:07.000 --> 01:09.000
Examiner: We're done.

01:10.000 --> 01:13.000
Examiner: Constant K, you can pick up your bonus.

01:15.000 --> 01:16.000
K: Thank you, sir.

01:17.000 --> 01:19.000
System: Caution. Keep clear here.

01:20.000 --> 01:22.000
System: Caution. Keep clear here.
